      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let’s get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle and preheat the grill to high</p><p>Chop <strong>half </strong>your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>remaining whole cherry tomatoes</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray under the grill until serving</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
