      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
